


# How to recreate this documentation



# Install Sphinx and Its Dependencies in your python environment


# Navigate to the root directory of the documentation folder

# Run the command ``` sphinx-apidoc -f -o /folderpath/to/autotemp/clone /source/api```

This regenerates the documentation taken from function and module docstrings and creates the necessary rst files that are embedded into the web application as documentation

# Run make html

Creates html files 